sentences: Kemal Doğulu (born 14 October 1979) is a Turkish photographer, hairdresser, stylist and singer.
Doğulu was born in 1979 in Mersin as the eldest child of Nur and Rasim Doğulu.
In 2006, he met Hande Yener and worked as her photographer and image consultant for her EP Hande Maxi.
In January 2008, he released his first EP, titled 1 Yerde, which featured elements of electronic music.
It was broadcast on MTV Türkiye in February 2008.
The next month it was shown all on MTV channels across the globe, after which the song entered the World Chart Exskpress (World Top 10) chart and rose to the first place in April.
